    <string name="about_title_4">Safe Lock</string>
    <string name="about_content_4_1">Safe Lock - is application on your Gear device to input key.</string>
    <string name="about_content_4_2"> - Rotate bezel to correct number.</string>
    <string name="about_content_4_3"> - Press in the middle of screen to pick number.</string>
    <string name="about_content_4_4"> - Double press in the middle of screen to erase previous number.</string>
    <string name="about_content_4_5"> - Press back button to send key to phone and exit. Notice that after being 5 seconds in background your application will do the same.</string>
